run c++ program:
g++ -o output_name program_file.cpp -std=c++11

or

g++ -o program_file.cpp -std=c++11 (this defaults to a.out)


open terminal;
run ./output_name or a.out

##############################################################
For debugging:
g++ -g output_name program_file.cpp -std=c++11

or

g++ -g program_file.cpp -std=c++11


open terminal;
run gdb a.out
or
run ddd a.out

